<BLOCK1><TI>ORDER MADE AFTER APPLICATION</TI>
<P>ON THE APPLICATION of the Defendant, Lengara Ventures Inc., coming on for hearing at Vancouver Law Courts on Friday, July 6, 2012 and on hearing Adele L. Burchart, counsel for Lengara Ventures Inc., and P. Daniel Le Dressay, counsel for NGC Management Ltd. and Alfredo Hermano, and on reading the material fifed;</P>
<P>THIS COURT ORDERS that:</P>
<P>1. The Defendant, Lengara Ventures Inc., is granted leave to file the Counterclaim attached as Schedule &ldquo;A&rdquo; to this Order, and that the filed Counterclaim shall be served on the Plaintiff within seven (7) days of receipt of same by the Defendant.</P>
<P>2. The application of the Defendant to file the proposed Third Party Notice is dismissed.</P>
<P>3. The Plaintiff, NGM Management Ltd., shall post security for costs in the amount of $20,000.00 and that this proceeding is stayed until said security is posted.</P>
