<P>1. I am a legal assistant with Munroe &amp; Company, the solicitors for the plaintiff, NGC Management Ltd. (&ldquo;NGC&rdquo;), and therefore have personal knowledge of the facts and matters referred to in this affidavit except where the same are stated to be made upon information and belief and, where so stated, I verily believe the same to be true.</P>
