<P>1. I am a legal assistant at Rosberg Sawatzky LLP, solicitors for the defendant, Lengara Ventures Inc., now know as Walker Group Ventures Inc. (&ldquo;Lengara&rdquo;), and as such have personal knowledge of the facts and matters hereinafter deposed to, save and except where such information is stated to be on information and belief, and I verily believe that information to be true.</P>
<P>2. I make this affidavit in response to the 1<SUP>st</SUP> affidavit of Garrett Munroe, counsel for NGC Management Ltd., now know as NGC Constructors Ltd. (&ldquo;NGC&rdquo;), made on November 10, 2017.</P>
<P>3. I am advised by Alexandra Bradshaw at Mainland Reporting, Mediation and Transcription, that Sarah Lavrisa ordered a transcript of the chambers hearing before Master Muir on July 6, 2017, on August 25, 2017.</P>
