<P1>b, Attached and marked as Exhibit &ldquo;<BOLD>B</BOLD>&rdquo; to this my Affidavit is a true copy of an Application Response dated, and filed on, October 17, 2017, in proceedings involving NGC, bearing the signature of Mr. Munroe.</P1></P>
<P>6. Attached and marked collectively as Exhibit &ldquo;<BOLD>C</BOLD>&rdquo; to this my Affidavit is a true copy of our fax call reports of service of the defendant's unfiled and filed Notice of Application dated October 12, 2017, and my Affidavit #3, upon NGC; unfiled copies were served only by facsimile at 3:45PM, and filed copies were by facsimile at 5: 26PM and by courier, on October 12, 2017.</P>
