<P>8. Attached and marked collectively as Exhibit &ldquo;<BOLD>E</BOLD>&rdquo; to this my Affidavit is a true copy of correspondence from Mr. Munroe to Mr. Rosberg, dated November 16, 2017, and correspondence from Mr. Rosberg and revised orders, couriered to Mr. Munroe on November 17, 2017.</P>
